  tempor incididunt ut laaliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam,
  quis nosalsdkfd kdls</p>
</div>

<a href="/gallery/{{mainPhoto.id}}">
  <div id="main-photo" style="background:url({{mainPhoto.link}}); background-size: cover; background-position: center"></div>
